gui.mxtune.button.save.help03: A Title and at least one instrument tab must have a melody line. Empty instrument tabs are not allowed.

tooltip.mxtune.music_venue_tool_block.he: Used to manage mxTune Venues. mxTunes played within a Venue are only heard by players while inside. mxTunes played Outside the Venue are not heard by players within.
tooltip.mxtune.music_venue_tool_item.shi: Right Click two blocks to define a Venue. Minimum size 2x2x2. Venues cannot intersect.
SHIFT+Right Click block to Reset back to Start.
To REMOVE a venue, stand *inside* it and Right Click any block. *(Head and Body)*
Survival: Owners may remove their own Venues. OP/Creative players can remove any Venue.
Venues are only visible when this tool is on the HotBar.
